  "description": "A full 5e character sheet that plays: a portrait, tap-to-roll abilities, saves and skills as proficiency cards (tick proficiency or expertise per skill), typable HP, death saves, charges, spell slots, and an inventory page with purse and attunement. Cantrips, personality, and backstory arrive pre-rolled.",
