    { "type": "paragraph", "label": "How it rolls", "text": "Tap any ability, save, skill, or attack to roll it — modifiers read live, so raising a score updates every roll. In edit mode every save and skill card carries proficiency and expertise checkboxes (expertise doubles your proficiency bonus, per the rules); tick yours and the card folds the bonus in. HP is typable at the table, hit dice and death saves tick, and ＋ action offers attacks, checks, saves, and charge boxes. Level up: bump Prof and Hit Points, and everything follows." },
